# Privacy Policy for Cash Denomination

**Effective Date:** 14 February 2026

OneStop (“we”, “our”, or “us”) built the **Cash Denomination** app as a utility application. This app is provided as-is and is intended for offline use.

Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains what information is collected, how it is used, and how it is protected.

---

## 1. Information We Collect
The **Cash Denomination** app does **not collect or transmit any personal data** to external servers.

The app may allow users to optionally enter:
- Name
- Company name

This information is:
- Stored **locally on the device only**
- Used solely to personalize the app experience
- **Never shared**, uploaded, or transmitted

---

## 2. Data Storage
All data entered in the app is stored locally on your device using internal app storage.

We do not have access to this data.

---

## 3. Internet Usage
The **Cash Denomination** app:
- Does **not require an internet connection**
- Does **not send or receive data** from any server

---

## 4. Third-Party Services
This app does **not use**:
- Ads
- Analytics tools
- Crash reporting services
- Third-party SDKs that collect user data

---

## 5. Data Security
Since all information remains on your device, the security of your data depends on your device’s operating system and security settings.

---

## 6. Children’s Privacy
The **Cash Denomination** app does not knowingly collect any personal information from children under the age of 13.

---

## 7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated effective date.

